"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月12-13日，由凤凰网主办，凤凰网财经承办的“2021凤凰网财经峰会”在上海举办。复旦大学泛海国际金融学院执行院长、金融学教授钱军在现场分享了当下金融的风险和机遇。谈到[虚拟货币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)时，他表示以[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)为代表的虚拟币不是黄金，不是主流资产，更不是规避通胀风险的最好资产。\",\"timestamp\":1639306965,\"title\":\"复旦大学钱军：比特币不是黄金,不是规避通胀风险的最好资产\"},\"digest\":\"EpeMDVeuCZt42l-UKkbUFPULK2wClWosK9QmMqPtkVY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xaCE5dE479a89c9a586f3dF5B2D0FEcb915388b7F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LU0DMlPNorGq-rajmPp7weKcDnNnaMwFlPcWa0nuFtg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FdsIWcokfjjviqLVKlpAOe0yCucFOjIvuAKwk0ygDnc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"66mxsk8B-_TdvW613DxBSUIPeE91rkZ-X-20ErnI_GZKNpNqj4vzsx77-R72aBbdSeDgMHVYRzIVJX39GzC2Ww\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1f0025f88789d05d2eb0c433d59299a72f39ee340e21e98ffcfcbd8772e80381170b0ffa8e69ee1dfd2c9b65b58ed35460e6401b831b7443176fbb160014fa221c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LU0DMlPNorGq-rajmPp7weKcDnNnaMwFlPcWa0nuFtg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FdsIWcokfjjviqLVKlpAOe0yCucFOjIvuAKwk0ygDnc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"EpeMDVeuCZt42l-UKkbUFPULK2wClWosK9QmMqPtkVY\"}"